name: Before I Really Lose It With You! Coloring Page
description:
Ever want to do a collab with SHT!? Probably not! But if for some reason you have wanted to, well, now you can!

Purchase this coloring page print and do what you will with it! 

When done, snap a picture, send it to me and ill share it on your favorite social media sites!

name: Before I Really Lose It With You! (Regular 2)
description:
This is a mixed media/hand embellished screen printed piece! The solid black and "stitching" is screenprinted, then parts were hand cut out with an exacto blade! Just like you would a stencil! Finally, different types of patterned and textured scrapbook paper was then glued behind the piece to fill the voids! Each piece is an edition of 1!

The size is 16x20 and its an edition of 1!

*These will be shipped flat!*
